(1520, '2006-09-29', 'Defcon Available Now At Steamgames.com', '<div class=\"post_content\" id=\"content_767\" style=\"display: none;\">
<p>Introversion today launched DEFCON, a new online strategy game from the creators of the award-winning Darwinia, via Steam, Valve\'s pioneering broadband platform for games and digital content.<br/><br/>Available now for just $14.95, DEFCON is an online, competitive, multiplayer strategy game based around the theme of global thermonuclear war. The player assumes the role of a General hidden deep within an underground bunker, his mission being to successfully exterminate the enemy\'s civilian population whilst simultaneously disabling the enemy\'s ability to retaliate.<br/><br/>For more information, please visit <a href=\"http://www.steamgames.com/\">www.steamgames.com</a>.</p>
<br clear=\"left\"/>
</div>'),
