(1520, '2007-04-19', NULL, '<div class=\"details\" id=\"April 19, 2007\" style=\"display: block;\">
Changes/Additions
	<ul>
<li> Cross platform compatability added. PC/Mac/Linux versions are now network compatible with each other</li> <li> AmBX support added</li> <li> City Populations game option added</li> <li> \"Can\'t place here\" circles now show when territory display is on</li> <li> Can no longer set blank or overlong player name</li> <li> Word wrapping algorithm improved (most obvious in the chat window)</li> <li> The game start countdown will now abort if a player leaves</li> <li> Removed unused \"Level 8\" button in Tutorial interface</li> <li> Users can no longer join incompatible games, even if they really try</li> </ul>
Bug fixes
	<ul>
<li> Fixed very rare cause where a plane could crash over a ground target and effectively nuke it, causing population death or building destruction</li> <li> Mods no longer disappear from the list when deactivated</li> <li> Attempting to set a very long username no longer crashes DEFCON</li> </ul>
</div>'),
(1520, '2007-04-19', 'Defcon Update Released', '<div class=\"post_content\" id=\"content_1015\" style=\"display: none;\">
